STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Carlos M. LOPEZ, Defendant-Petitioner. C-1015 September Term 2016
079331 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-4552-14 and A0593-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
